strings:
<voice_0x0100162D><se_high>Jessica: This doesn't look good!
Argh! We've got to get out of here!

<voice_0x0100162E><se_low>Yangus: Uh, uh-oh! We're in trouble now!
Time to leg it!

<voice_0x0100162F><se_def>Angelo: Well I knew we'd bring the house down, but I didn't think it would happen quite so literally!
This show's over!

<voice_0x01001630><se_high>Red: Thanks a bunch, you lot, takin' the easy way out! Well I ain't dyin' now! Not after beatin' that dirty great lump! I'm gettin' out of 'ere if it
kills me!
<voice_0x01001631><se_low>Morrie: We take out the capo di tutti capi, and he takes out the castello, ay? Time to do the splits, amici!
